data.text: Jisas bɨne anep umɨgan ak suk agek apel agak, Nɨbop kɨles awl ñɨl agen, nɨbi kɨles yad ak dɨl amnɨmɨb agak. Dad amɨl, kɨcheki walɨjpal binɨb mulɨk sɨkek mɨdebal okok agem, pɨlɨk amnɨgel agak. Binɨb tap gup okok gem suŋ lɨnɨmuŋ agak. God binɨb dɨl kɨlop kod yenɨgab takaw ak kɨlop agñɨnɨmɨb agak.
9.3-5 Luk 10.4-11 Pen amnɨg, yɨl kodɨm, mani, wad, chech, tap ñɨŋeb tap okok sek dad ma amnɨmɨb agak. Yokɨp amnɨmɨb agak.
9.4 Mat 10.11, Mak 6.10 Kal olap amjakem nɨbop agdenɨgel, kɨli ayɨp kɨn tep gɨl, amnɨg gɨnɨmɨb ñɨn ak nep amnɨmɨb agak.

9.5 Mat 10.14, Mak 6.11, Apo 13.51 Pen man wakay ogɨnap amem nɨbop ma agdenɨgel, man anɨb ak kelɨg amnɨg kɨlop agɨnɨmɨb, Takaw tep ak dad opun ma dɨpɨm tek, man nɨbop awl apon sɨlkul dayday tob chɨnop dup ak wik yokɨl amobun agɨnɨmɨb agak. Wik yokɨl amnɨmɨb agak.
9.6 Mak 6.12 Anɨb agaknɨŋ, kɨli man sɨkol okok amɨl, takaw teplep ak agñɨlɨg binɨb tap gak okok gel suŋ lolɨgup.
Pen binɨb okok, Jisas tɨtay gak takaw anɨb ak ag amɨl apɨl gɨlaknɨŋ, gapman bɨnonɨm Helod nɨŋɨd gos kuŋay yɨbɨl nɨgak. Binɨb ogɨnap agɨlak, Jon Bɨ Ñɨg Pakñeb tepayaŋ tɨkjakup agɨlak.
Ogɨnap agɨlak, Bɨ God gos ñek agñeb ned nɨb Yilayja mɨseŋ owup agɨlak. Ogɨnap agɨlak, Bɨ God gos ñek agñeb bɨlel olap tepayaŋ tɨkjakup agɨlak.
9.9 Luk 23.8 Anɨb agel, gapman bɨnonɨm Helod agak, Jon nop kuŋam tɨken kumub anɨb ak tek, bɨ anɨb an apɨl mɨdaknɨŋ agebal ak agak. Pen yad nop nɨgɨnɨm agɨl gos ak nɨgak.
Pen Jisas bɨ takaw nop dad ameb okok, kɨli adɨkɨd apɨl, tap tɨtay gɨlak tek takaw ak, nop agñɨlak. Agñel Jisas man wakay olap am ke mɨdon agɨl, kɨlop poŋɨd taun Betsayda amnɨg saŋɨdɨlak.
Kanɨb nab okok amnɨlaknɨŋ, binɨb kuŋay nep kɨdek gɨlak. Kɨdek gɨl apjakel, kɨlop Tep opɨm agɨl, God binɨb dɨl kɨlop kod yenɨgab takaw ak kɨlop agñak. Agñɨlɨg, binɨb tap gak okok gek suŋ lak.

Pen dugep sub saŋɨd amnak won ak, bɨ takaw nop dad ameb anep umɨgan ak apɨl Jisas nop agɨlak, Okol man nep nab okok mɨdobun nen, binɨb okol agyokɨnɨmɨn agɨlak. Agyoke, kal okok keke amɨl, tap mɨdup kɨli okok pɨyow nɨgɨlɨg, kɨnɨgel mɨgan ak pɨyow nɨgɨlɨg gɨlaŋ agɨlak.

Anɨb agelak Jisas agak, Nɨbi ke kɨlop tap mɨdup ñɨnɨmɨb agak. Agek agɨlak, Chɨn tap ñɨŋeb kuŋay ma mɨdeb agɨlak. Yokɨp bilet anep mamɨd ak mɨdɨl, kubsal omɨŋal mɨdɨl gup agɨlak. Nad tay gos nepan agɨlak? Binɨb awl kuŋay mɨdebal ak, chɨn am tap ñɨŋeb kɨlop ogɨnap taw dad ownɨgun agɨlak?
Ñɨn anɨb ak, binɨb apnan gɨlak okok, bin okok sek ñapay okok sek mel, bɨ okok nep nɨm 5,000 tek yelak.
Agek agak tek gel,
ne bilet anep mamɨd ak, kubsal omɨŋal ak sek dɨl, kɨlan gɨl nɨŋɨd, God nop tep agɨl, tɨpag bɨne okok kɨlop ñek, kɨli pen dɨlɨg, binɨb okok kɨlop bɨlok ñɨlak.
Ñelak ñɨb dad amɨl, ñɨbdɨnɨgel tek ma yek. Ñɨb dad amɨl apɨl gel, kɨdek Jisas bɨne okok wad anep umɨgan ak yɨgel aplan jakak.
Pen ñɨn olap Jisas ne God ayɨp agɨlɨg mɨdɨl, bɨne okok kɨlop agnɨŋɨd agak, Binɨb yokɨp okok yɨp an agɨl nepal agak?

9.19 Mat 14.1-2, Mak 6.14-15, Luk 9.7-8 Agek agɨlak, Binɨb ogɨnap nep Jon Bɨ Ñɨg Pakñeb ak agɨl nepal agɨlak. Ogɨnap, bɨ God gos ñek agñeb ned nɨb Yilayja agɨl nepal agɨlak. Ogɨnap, bɨ God gos ñek agñeb bɨlel olap tepayaŋ tɨkjakup agɨl nepal agɨlak.
9.20 Mat 16.15-16, Mak 8.29, Jon 6.68-69 Agelak, kɨlop pen agak, Nɨbi ke yɨp bɨ an agɨl nepɨm agak? Agek Pita agak, Nad Bɨ God nop aglup ak, chɨnop dɨl kod yenɨgaban ak agak.
Anɨb agek, Jisas kɨlop agak, Takaw anɨb ak, binɨb ogɨnap kɨlop ma agñɨnɨmɨb agak.

9.22 Mat 16.21, 17.22, Mak 8.31, 9.31, Luk 9.44, 18.32-33 Anɨb agɨl takaw olap pen agak, Bɨ Olap Ñɨne nop yul awl yɨbɨl ñɨnɨgabal agak. Bɨ Juda bɨawl takaw tɨg asɨkep okok, bɨ God nop sɨbogep bɨawl okok, bɨ kɨli Mosis takaw ñu kɨl tɨkak ak nɨgtep gep okok, kɨli nop ma dɨnɨgabal agak. Mɨlɨk nɨŋɨd, ñaglɨnɨgabal ak pen, ñɨn omɨŋal nokom mɨdɨl, tepayaŋ tɨkjakɨnɨgab agak.
Pen Jisas, ne bɨne okok sek, binɨb yelak okok sek, kɨlop agak, Binɨb an yɨp kɨdek gonɨmuŋ, gos ne ak kelɨgɨl, mab bak kumak chɨn ak mɨnek mɨnek dad ajɨl, yɨp chɨgɨl kɨdek gɨnɨmuŋ agak.

9.24 Mat 10.39, Luk 17.33, Jon 12.25 Binɨb an ne ke mɨdɨl, mɨdtep gin agɨnɨgab ak, kɨdek mɨd tɨmel gɨnɨgab agak. Pen binɨb an yɨp dɨl, yɨp tap tay gɨnɨgab takaw ma mɨdeb agɨnɨgab ak, mɨdtep gɨnɨgab agak.
9.25 Mat 16.26, Mak 8.36 Pen bɨ tap lum awl yɨl mɨdupsek dɨnɨgab ak, kɨdek ne tɨtay dɨl yenɨgab agak?

9.26 Mat 10.33, Mak 8.38, Luk 12.9, 2 Ti 2.12 Bɨ an yɨp nebeŋ gɨnɨmuŋ tek lek nɨŋɨd, Jisas nop ma nepin agɨnɨgab ak, kɨdek Bɨ Olap Ñɨne, ne Bapi mɨlek awl ñɨlapɨl dɨl, ensel okok mɨlek awl dɨl ownɨgab ñɨn ak, nop pen abe Bapi nop agɨnɨgab, Nop ma nepin agɨnɨgab agak.
Pen nɨbop nɨŋɨd yɨbɨl agebin agak. Binɨb mɨñɨl mɨdebɨm okok ogɨnap ma kumnɨgabɨm won ak, God binɨb dɨl kɨlop kod yenɨgab ñɨn anɨb ak nɨgɨnɨgabɨm agak.
Jisas anɨb agɨl, ñɨn anep jel ak tek mɨdɨl, Pita, Jon, Jemis kɨlop poŋɨd, God ayɨp agɨnɨg dum olap amnak.
Amɨl, God ayɨp ag mɨdɨlaknɨŋ, jomulɨk nop ak ke yɨbɨl lɨl, chech nop ak kayɨg gɨl ñɨñakol gɨlɨg yek.
Anɨgaknɨŋ, bɨ bɨlel yelɨgɨpil, Mosis ayɨp Yilayja ayɨp,
9.31 Mat 17.3, 17.9, Mak 9.4, 9.9, Luk 9.22, 13.33 God mɨlek awl ak dɨl apɨl, Jisas kɨdek am Jelusalem yek nop mab bak alaŋ chɨpɨl pak tɨbɨk lel kumnɨgab takaw ak ag yelak.
9.32 Mat 17.2-3, Mak 9.2-4, Jon 1.14, 2 Pi 1.16-18 Ag yelaknɨŋ, Pita, Jon, Jemis kɨlop wɨsɨn apek kɨn yelak ak pen tɨkjakɨl nɨgɨlak, Jisas mɨlek awl ak, Mosis ayɨp Yilayja ayɨp jakɨl yelak.

Bɨ omɨŋal ayɨp amnɨg gɨleknɨŋ, Pita gos nɨgtep gɨl mel, Jisas nop agak, Bɨawl. Chɨn awl mɨdon tep yɨbɨl gup agak. Nad yaw age, kal sɨkol bad omɨŋal nokom gun agak. Nep olap, Mosis nop olap, Yilayja nop olap agak.
Anɨb agaknɨŋ, won anɨb anep wɨsɨp awl ak kɨlop apɨl mɨdupsek yu gaknɨŋ, pɨlɨkɨlak.
9.35 Ais 42.1, Mat 3.17, 12.18, 17.5, Mak 1.11, 9.7, Luk 3.22 Pen takaw olap wɨsɨp nab anɨb ak nɨb apɨl agak, Ñɨ yad, yad nop aglɨpin agak. Takaw agɨnɨmuŋ tek nɨgɨnɨmɨb agak.
Takaw agjuwek nɨgɨlak, bɨ omɨŋal ma yelek. Jisas ne nep yek. Pen dum alaŋ mɨdel tap gek nɨgɨlak anɨb ak, ñɨn anɨb ak binɨb ogɨnap kɨlop ma agñɨlak.
Pen mɨnek, Jisas ayɨp bɨne okok ayɨp dum alaŋ kelɨgɨl, kanɨb nab okok apyapɨlɨg nɨgɨlak, binɨb kuŋay yɨbɨl Jisas nop pɨyowel apek.
Bɨ olap binɨb kuŋay nep nab anɨb ak suk awl agɨl agak, Tisa. Ñɨ yad nokom awl nɨgan agak.
Kɨcheki ak pelnep abaŋ lɨ mɨdɨl, nop gek suk awl agɨl, gɨdam pakɨl, kosɨb asɨb apɨl, kum dam nab lɨlɨg owup agak. Nop anɨgɨl pel pelnep gek gek nɨm, mɨdtep ma gup agak.
Bɨnak okok kɨlop takaw kɨles gɨl apin, Kɨcheki mɨdeb ak agyokɨm agɨl apin ak pen, kɨli agyok mel nɨŋɨd kelɨgɨpal agak.

Anɨb agek Jisas agak, Binɨb lum awl mɨdebɨm okok, nɨbi anɨgɨpɨm teplep mel agak. Ñɨn akal gos lɨnɨgɨnɨgabɨm agak? Ma yɨbɨl nepɨm anɨb ak, yad ñɨn tɨtay nɨb ayɨp mɨdɨl, mɨŋel nɨbop ak dad ajenɨm agak? Anɨb agɨl, bɨ anɨb anop agak, Ñɨ nad anɨb ak dad sɨŋawl owan agak.
Agek dad owaknɨŋ, kɨcheki ak ñɨ anɨb anop kɨles gɨl pɨpag yokek gɨdam pakak. Jisas pen kɨcheki anop ag gek, ke amnaknɨŋ, ñɨ anɨb ak ñɨ yɨbɨl lek, dɨ nap nop ñak.
Binɨb ap yelak okok, God kɨles anɨb ak nɨŋɨd judɨlak.
9.44 Mat 16.21, 17.22, Mak 8.31, 9.31, Luk 9.22, 18.32-33 Takaw agebin awl tɨmud pakɨl, nɨgtep yɨbɨl gɨnɨmɨb agak. Wulep mɨdeb, Bɨ Olap Ñɨne nop mɨmug nɨŋɨd bɨ ogɨnap kɨlop ñɨnɨgabal agak.
9.45 Mak 9.32, Luk 2.50, 18.34 Takaw agak anɨb ak, kɨli tɨk nɨgep tek ma lek pɨlɨkɨl, Jisas nop ma agnɨgɨlak.
Bɨne okok kɨli ke ag amɨl apɨl gɨl agɨlak, Yad bɨawl mɨden, Yad bɨawl mɨden agɨlak.
Jisas bɨne okok gos tɨmel nɨgɨlak anɨb ak ke nɨŋɨd, ñɨsɨkol yɨbɨl olap dap ne yek bak sɨŋak lɨl

9.48 Mat 10.40, 23.11-12, Mak 9.37, Luk 10.16, Jon 12.44, 13.20 agak, Binɨb yɨp gos nɨŋɨd, ñɨsɨkol kɨlop anɨb ak tek dɨnɨgabal okok, kɨlop nep mel, yɨp abe dɨnɨgabal agak. Pen yɨp dɨnɨgabal okok, yɨp nokom mel, Bapi yɨp agyokek ownek ak nop abe dɨnɨgabal agak. Bɨ olap nab nɨbi pi okok yɨb ma mɨdeb ak, ne yɨb mɨdeb agak.
Anɨb agek Jon agak, Bɨawl. Chɨn nopun, bɨ olap yɨb nep ak agɨl kɨcheki walɨjpal tap okok agyokup agak. Pen chɨn ayɨp ma ajɨpun tek, nop anɨb ak ma gɨnɨmɨn apun agak.
Agek Jisas agak, Taynen nop anɨb apɨm agak? Binɨb nɨbop mɨlɨk ma nepal okok bogɨlak nɨbi agak.
Pen God Jisas nop dad man ne alaŋ amnɨg gak ñɨn ak wulep mɨdaknɨŋ, Jisas Jelusalem amnin agɨl gos kɨles gɨl nɨgak.
Ak nɨm, bɨ ogɨnap kɨlop ned agyokɨl agak, Nɨbi ned amɨl, kɨneb tep yɨp ak nɨgenɨmɨb agak. Agek, kɨli am Samaliya binɨb kal olap amjakɨl agɨlak, Jisas kɨneb tep nop olap ag dam lɨm agɨlak.
9.53 Jon 4.9 Agel, binɨb man anɨb okok nɨgɨlak, Jisas Jelusalem amnɨg gek nɨm, kɨlop tep ma gek nop ma dɨlak.
9.54 2 Kin 1.9-16 Ma delak nɨŋɨd, bɨne Jemis ayɨp Jon ayɨp, Jisas nop agɨlek, Bɨawl. Chɨn mab mɨŋɨlaŋ wɨsɨp alaŋ nɨb ak agon apɨl, binɨb anɨgɨpal okok kɨlop yɨn gɨnɨmuŋ akaŋ agɨlek?
Anɨb agel, Jisas adɨkɨl kɨlop bɨ omɨŋal ag gak.
Anɨb agɨl, man anɨb ak kelɨgɨl man olap ke amnɨlak.
Pen kanɨb nab okok amnɨlaknɨŋ, bɨ olap apɨl Jisas nop agak, Man akal akal amnɨgaban okok, yad ayɨp nep ajonɨgabul agak.

Anɨb agek, Jisas nop agak, Yad ayɨp koslam ajenɨgaban agak. Chen ladek okok kal kɨli kɨneb ak, lum mɨgan okok mɨdeb agak. Yawl okok kal kɨli ak ke mɨdeb agak. Pen Bɨ Olap Ñɨne kal kɨneb ne ak ma mɨdeb agak.
Pen Jisas bɨ olap nop agak, Yɨp kode, yad ayɨp ajol agak. Agek, bɨ anɨb ak pen agak, Yɨp yaw age, yad ned bapi kumek nop kamɨl, nad ayɨp ajonɨgul agak.
Agek, Jisas nop agak, Binɨb pel ma mɨdebal okok, chɨp kumeb anɨb okok kamnɨgel agak. Nad pen am God binɨb dɨl kɨlop kod yenɨgab takaw ak kɨlop agñe amnaŋ agak.
Bɨ olap pen agak, Yad nad ayɨp nep ajonɨgabul ak pen, yɨp Yaw age, am ami bapi, mam ay yad okok kɨlop ñɨn pak sakɨl, agñɨl ownɨm agak.
Agek, Jisas nop agak, Bɨ olap God nop wog ak gɨñin agɨl apɨl, gos tɨmud awl ne ak, adɨkɨd tap ne binɨb ne okok amek, taydɨl God binɨb dɨl kɨlop kod yenɨgab ñɨn ak mɨdɨl, nop wog gɨñɨnɨgab agak.
